episodes.title: Isabella Young | Cults, Belief, Systematic Control
episodes.description: Isabella Young is a former cult member, author , and speaker dedicated to raising awareness about the psychological and emotional manipulation that can occur in cult-like environments. We dive deep into her personal journey, sharing how her early life in Australia — marked by emotional turmoil — shaped her understanding of love, relationships, and ultimately, her susceptibility to cult dynamics.
